ic pain, cardiovascular disease, Alzheimer’s disease, mechanisms of aging, epigenetics, novel scientific tools and methods, under-studied or unusual biological phenomena, and research on how biomedical research may be improved. Additionally, we are interested in research that supports the further development of plant-based meat replacements.'),(17131,670,'_focus_area_detail_content_1_content','field_60f7bf90c773e'),(17132,670,'focus_area_detail_content_1_aside_0_message','The Following Open Philanthropy staff oversee the Scientific Research program.'),(17133,670,'_focus_area_detail_content_1_aside_0_message','field_60f7c20cc7745'),(17134,670,'focus_area_detail_content_1_aside_0_staff','a:3:{i:0;s:3:\"366\";i:1;s:3:\"364\";i:2;s:3:\"360\";}'),(17135,670,'_focus_area_detail_content_1_aside_0_staff','field_60f7c09cc7743'),(17136,670,'focus_area_detail_content_1_aside_1_heading','Open calls for proposals'),(17137,670,'_focus_area_detail_content_1_aside_1_heading','field_60f7c263c7748'),(17138,670,'focus_area_detail_content_1_aside_1_content','We are open to receiving unsolicited short pre-proposals at <a href=\"mailto:science@openphilanthropy.org\">science@openphilanthropy.org</a>. We try to consider all proposals but are unable to respond in most cases.'),(17139,670,'_focus_area_detail_content_1_aside_1_content','field_60f7c246c7747'),(17140,670,'focus_area_detail_content_1_aside','a:2:{i:0;s:10:\"staff_list\";i:1;s:13:\"short_message\";}'),(17141,670,'_focus_area_detail_content_1_aside','field_60f7bfdbc7740'),(17142,670,'focus_area_detail_content_2_heading','Scientific Research, at a glance'),(17143,670,'_focus_area_detail_content_2_heading','field_60f87b900096a'),(17144,670,'focus_area_detail_content_2_statistics_0_type','custom'),(17145,670,'_focus_area_detail_content_2_statistics_0_type','field_60f87c88d9f31'),(17146,670,'focus_area_detail_content_2_statistics_0_title','Portfolio<br> Areas'),(17147,670,'_focus_area_detail_content_2_statistics_0_title','field_60f87b