Once we understand the research gaps in these fields, we assess which gaps are underfunded and seem most amenable to progress if funded. Often as part of this process, we will attend scientific conferences and interview scientists as advisors, peer reviewers, or potential grantees. For more information, see our Guide for Grant Seekers.\r\n\r\nSome aspects of the following topics are currently of particular interest: broad spectrum antiviral drugs, universal influenza vaccine, basic immunology, chronic pain, cardiovascular disease, Alzheimer’s disease, mechanisms of aging, epigenetics, novel scientific tools and methods, under-studied or unusual biological phenomena, and research on how biomedical research may be improved. Additionally, we are interested in research that supports the further development of plant-based meat replacements.'),(17946,691,'_focus_area_detail_content_1_content','field_60f7bf90c773e'),(17947,691,'focus_area_detail_content_1_aside_0_message','The Following Open Philanthropy staff oversee the Scientific Research program.'),(17948,691,'_focus_area_detail_content_1_aside_0_message','field_60f7c20cc7745'),(17949,691,'focus_area_detail_content_1_aside_0_staff','a:3:{i:0;s:3:\"366\";i:1;s:3:\"364\";i:2;s:3:\"360\";}'),(17950,691,'_focus_area_detail_content_1_aside_0_staff','field_60f7c09cc7743'),(17951,691,'focus_area_detail_content_1_aside_1_heading','Open calls for proposals'),(17952,691,'_focus_area_detail_content_1_aside_1_heading','field_60f7c263c7748'),(17953,691,'focus_area_detail_content_1_aside_1_content','We are open to receiving unsolicited short pre-proposals at <a href=\"mailto:science@openphilanthropy.org\">science@openphilanthropy.org</a>. We try to consider all proposals but are unable to respond in most cases.'),(17954,691,'_focus_area_detail_content_1_aside_1_content','field_60f7c246c7747'),(17955,691,'focus_area_detail_content_1_aside','a:2:{i:0;s:10:\"staff_list\";i:1;s:13:\"short_message\";}'),(17956,691,'_focus_area_detail_con