cts of the following topics are currently of particular interest: broad spectrum antiviral drugs, universal influenza vaccine, basic immunology, chronic pain, cardiovascular disease, Alzheimer’s disease, mechanisms of aging, epigenetics, novel scientific tools and methods, under-studied or unusual biological phenomena, and research on how biomedical research may be improved. Additionally, we are interested in research that supports the further development of plant-based meat replacements.'),(18463,713,'_focus_area_detail_content_1_content','field_60f7bf90c773e'),(18464,713,'focus_area_detail_content_1_aside_0_message','The Following Open Philanthropy staff oversee the Scientific Research program.'),(18465,713,'_focus_area_detail_content_1_aside_0_message','field_60f7c20cc7745'),(18466,713,'focus_area_detail_content_1_aside_0_staff','a:3:{i:0;s:3:\"366\";i:1;s:3:\"364\";i:2;s:3:\"360\";}'),(18467,713,'_focus_area_detail_content_1_aside_0_staff','field_60f7c09cc7743'),(18468,713,'focus_area_detail_content_1_aside_1_heading','Open calls for proposals'),(18469,713,'_focus_area_detail_content_1_aside_1_heading','field_60f7c263c7748'),(18470,713,'focus_area_detail_content_1_aside_1_content','We are open to receiving unsolicited short pre-proposals at <a href=\"mailto:science@openphilanthropy.org\">science@openphilanthropy.org</a>. We try to consider all proposals but are unable to respond in most cases.'),(18471,713,'_focus_area_detail_content_1_aside_1_content','field_60f7c246c7747'),(18472,713,'focus_area_detail_content_1_aside','a:2:{i:0;s:10:\"staff_list\";i:1;s:13:\"short_message\";}'),(18473,713,'_focus_area_detail_content_1_aside','field_60f7bfdbc7740'),(18474,713,'focus_area_detail_content_2_heading','Global Health & Development, at a glance'),(18475,713,'_focus_area_detail_content_2_heading','field_60f87b900096a'),(18476,713,'focus_area_detail_content_2_statistics_0_type','custom'),(18477,713,'_focus_area_detail_content_2_statistics_0_type','field_60f87c88d9f31')